            <section id="sec-valuation" class="content-section fade-in hidden">
                <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-stone-900 mb-2">4단계: 가치 평가 (Valuation)</h2>
                    <p class="text-stone-600 mb-6 md:mb-8 text-base md:text-lg border-l-4 border-blue-900 pl-4">SOTP 및 EV/EBITDA 멀티플을 적용. 지배구조 리스크와 채권 희석을 가혹하게 반영한 내재 가치입니다.</p>

                    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4 md:gap-6 mb-8">
                        <div class="col-span-1 lg:col-span-2 bg-white p-5 md:p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-stone-200 order-2 lg:order-1">
                            <h3 class="font-bold text-stone-900 mb-4">가치 평가 방법론 (Methodology)</h3>
                            <div class="space-y-4 text-sm text-stone-700">
                                <div><strong class="text-blue-900">1. SOTP & EV/EBITDA:</strong> 장치 산업 특유의 막대한 감가상각비 착시를 제거하고 실질 현금창출력을 평가하기 위해 EV/EBITDA 모델 채택.</div>
                                <div><strong class="text-blue-900">2. Target Multiple (26.4x):</strong> AI 전력 르네상스를 공유하는 GE Vernova 및 MHI의 2026F 평균 멀티플 적용.</div>
                                <div><strong class="text-blue-900">3. 가혹한 디스카운트 적용:</strong> 밥캣 합병 사태에 따른 <strong>징벌적 지배구조 할인율(30~40%)</strong> 부과 및 3억 불 해외 전환사채 전량 보통주 전환(희석) 최악의 가정 수립.</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-span-1 bg-stone-900 text-white p-6 md:p-8 rounded-xl shadow-md flex flex-col justify-center items-center relative overflow-hidden order-1 lg:order-2">
                            <h3 class="text-stone-300 font-medium mb-1">Base Target Price</h3>
                            <div class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black mb-2" id="display-target-price">104,000<span class="text-base md:text-lg font-normal ml-1">KRW</span></div>
                            <div class="text-sm text-stone-400 mt-4 flex justify-between w-full border-t border-stone-700 pt-3">
                                <span>Applied EBITDA</span>
                                <span id="display-eps" class="font-bold text-white">2.57T KRW</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="text-sm text-stone-400 flex justify-between w-full mt-2">
                                <span>Target EV/EBITDA</span>
                                <span id="display-pe" class="font-bold text-white">26.4x</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <h3 class="font-bold text-stone-900 mb-4 text-lg md:text-xl">시나리오 분석 (터치해보세요)</h3>
                    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-3 md:gap-4">
                        <div class="flex-1 border-2 border-stone-200 rounded-xl p-4 md:p-5 cursor-pointer hover:border-red-400 transition-colors scenario-card" data-scenario="bear">
                            <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-2">
                                <span class="bg-red-100 text-red-800 text-[10px] md:text-xs font-bold px-2 py-1 rounded">BEAR CASE</span>
                                <span class="font-black text-base md:text-lg text-stone-800">65,000 원</span>
                            </div>
                            <p class="text-xs text-stone-600 mb-3 hidden md:block">미국 인프라 투자 심리 급랭 및 자회사 지배구조 분쟁 격화 (강력한 하방 안전 마진)</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex-1 border-2 border-blue-600 bg-blue-50 rounded-xl p-4 md:p-5 cursor-pointer transition-colors scenario-card active-scenario" data-scenario="base">
                            <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-2">
                                <span class="bg-blue-600 text-white text-[10px] md:text-xs font-bold px-2 py-1 rounded">BASE CASE</span>
                                <span class="font-black text-base md:text-lg text-blue-900">104,000 원</span>
                            </div>
