                        </div>
                        <div class="flex-1 border-2 border-stone-200 rounded-xl p-4 md:p-5 cursor-pointer hover:border-emerald-500 transition-colors scenario-card" data-scenario="bull">
                            <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-2">
                                <span class="bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-800 text-[10px] md:text-xs font-bold px-2 py-1 rounded">BULL CASE</span>
                                <span class="font-black text-base md:text-lg text-stone-800">145,000 원</span>
                            </div>
                            <p class="text-xs text-stone-600 mb-3 hidden md:block">북미 빅테크 가스터빈 폭증 수주 및 웨스팅하우스 분쟁 타결로 대형 원전 조기화</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

        </main>
